name: Unidentified_Imperial_officer_(hangar_Fifteen-D)
content: A human female Imperial officer served in the Galactic Empire aboard the Executor, the flagship of the Sith Lord Darth Vader. At some point, the officer came to be associated with the resurgent criminal syndicate Crimson Dawn and worked undercover on the Executor for Lady Qi'ra. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, when the Executor was present in the Jekara system after Crimson's Dawn auction for the smuggler Han Solo, the officer allowed the Rebel Alliance YT-1300 light freighter Millennium Falcon to board the vessel as its crew attempted to recover Solo, who had been brought aboard the Executor. When questioned by General Leia Organa about why an Imperial officer would help them, the officer revealed her alliegance to Crimson Dawn.
